{
  "stem": "26142.16",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Those that were-- were naked were ordered to go into another room and to get out the room through a window, not a door.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The window was not too high, but you had to get out completely naked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the reason for that was that they wanted to make sure that nobody has anything hidden in the most intimate places.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I forgot to take my-- my silver-- silver chain off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was ripped off, ripped off the chain, and got hit over the head on top of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got showered and then they would, after the shower, they would throw to you a pair of pants, a pair of shoes, a shirt, and a jacket.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No-- no-- never mind if you are six foot tall or you are five foot tall or if you weigh 150 pounds or you weigh 75 pounds.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had-- we had to run with these.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came into our block where we were supposed to stay-- block number 20 in Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there, we started to-- a small guy had a big pair of shoes, a big guy had a small pair of shoes, a short guy had long pants, a long guy had short pants, and we had to try to, among ourselves, to even it out, to exchange it.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was lucky that I was able to get a pair of shoes that I could put on and-- and-- and-- and-- and some-- and some clothing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was not military shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those-- those were shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember, I think I-- I had-- I think those were shoes that they gave from people that-- that they-- they-- they gassed, that was leftover shoes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was all kinds.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
